# Liabilities Other Financial Liabilities Loan Capital Amount

## identifier
de1500

## type
float

## definition
Report the value of loan capital on issue by the reporting party as at the reporting date.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=Liabilities.OtherFinancialLiabilities.LoanCapital.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo6.02.00
- period=instant
